John%20Thune%2C%20fresh%20off%20our%20many%20victories%20over%20the%20past%20two%20weeks%20and%2C%20indeed%2C%206%20months%2C%20will%20cancel%20August%20recess%20(and%20long%20weekends!)%2C%20in%20order%20to%20get%20my%20incredible%20nominees%20confirmed%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2Fposts%2F114882283904953607%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20Truth%20Social%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20weekend.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20them%20badly!!!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThune%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmaxpcohen%2Fstatus%2F1947374259606519983%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20reporters%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bthinking%20about%26quot%3B%20canceling%20the%20recess%20and%20said%20that%20senators%20were%20working%20on%20getting%20as%20many%20nominees%20%26quot%3Bthrough%20the%20pipeline%26quot%3B%20as%20they%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20one%20other%20senator%20has%20said%20he's%20fully%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbsolutely%2C%20I'm%20willing%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Republican%20Sen.%20Roger%20Marshall%20of%20Kansas%20said%20on%20Fox%20News%20on%20Sunday.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20happy%20to%20stay%20here%20as%20long%20as%20we're%20working.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2020%20of%20Trump's%20diplomatic%20nominees%20are%20still%20awaiting%20confirmation%20votes.%20Among%20them%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkimberly-guilfoyle-trump-greece-ambassador-net-worth-financial-disclosure-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKimberly%20Guilfoyle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20nominated%20to%20serve%20as%20US%20Ambassador%20to%20Greece.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Trump%20is%20successful%2C%20senators%20will%20have%20to%20stick%20around%20for%20lots%20of%20in%20August%2C%20even%20while%20their%20House%20colleagues%20get%20to%20go%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20first%20time%20this%20has%20happened.%20In%202018%2C%20then-Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20Mitch%20McConnell%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmitch-mcconnell-cancels-congress-august-recess-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecanceled%20recess%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20similar%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.senate.gov%2Fartandhistory%2Fsenate-stories%2Fgive-us-a-summer-break.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESenate%20Historical%20Office%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20August%20recess%20evolved%20out%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20modernize%20the%20way%20that%20Congress%20worked%2C%20building%20in%20more%20predictable%20breaks%20in%20the%20schedule%20rather%20than%20remaining%20in%20session%20until%20work%20is%20finished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20especially%20popular%20with%20the%20spouses%20of%20members%20of%20Congress%2C%20who%20wanted%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20together%20as%20a%20family%20during%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20lawmakers%20do%20take%20vacations%20during%20the%20month%20of%20August%20or%20during%20other%20shorter%20recesses%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20they%20often%20find%20themselves%20busy%20with%20other%20work%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20includes%20constituent%20meetings%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchuck-edwards-town-hall-asheville-north-carolina-doge-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etown%20halls%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20during%20election%20years%2C%20lots%20of%20campaigning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Senate%20GOP%20source%20told%20BI%20on%20Monday%20that%20senators%20would%20likely%20prefer%20to%20be%20back%20in%20their%20home%20states%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-big-beautiful-bill-medicaid-taxes-maga-accounts-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBig%20Beautiful%20Bill%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20sprawling%20piece%20of%20fiscal%20and%20