0Containers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687aaecbf748d8c055f5e941%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3EMartin%20Barraud%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20cold%20warehouses%2C%20AI%20can%20prevent%20costly%20product%20damage%20and%20assist%20with%20worker%20safety.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECold-chain%20providers%20are%20exploring%20how%20digital%20twins%20and%20AI%20agents%20could%20improve%20efficiency.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fhow-ai-is-changing-everything-supply-chain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20AI%20Is%20Changing%20Everything%3A%20Supply%20Chain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20on%20innovations%20in%20logistics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20shipment%20of%20refrigerated%20or%20frozen%20goods%20arrives%20at%20a%20Lineage%20Logistics%20warehouse%2C%20machines%20spring%20into%20action.%20Computer-vision%20technology%20scans%20pallets%20and%20logs%20data%20on%20customers%2C%20product%20types%2C%20and%20item%20descriptions.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-target-use-ai-to-prevent-inventory-shortages-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-driven%20algorithms%3C%2Fa%3E%20combine%20shipment%20data%20with%20historical%20information%20to%20predict%20when%20a%20truck%20will%20take%20the%20goods%20out%20of%20the%20warehouse.%20The%20technology%20assigns%20pallets%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20warehouse%20based%20on%20how%20long%20they'll%20remain%20in%20the%20facility%20and%20directs%20the%20forklift%20operator%20where%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20level%20of%20technology%20can%20improve%20efficiency%20in%20any%20type%20of%20supply%20chain%2C%20but%20it's%20critical%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsee-inside-walmart-high-tech-refrigerated-grocery-warehouse-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecold%20warehouses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20goods%20like%20frozen%20foods%2C%20fresh%20produce%2C%20and%20pharmaceuticals%20are%20stored.%20A%20brief%20deviation%20in%20temperature%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20damage%20a%20shipment%2C%20and%20warehouse%20managers%20don't%20want%20workers%20spending%20hours%20without%20breaks%20in%20sub-zero%20conditions.%20This%20makes%20accuracy%20and%20productivity%20imperative%20in%20the%20cold%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERefrigeration%20and%20temperature-sensor%20technology%20have%20been%20integral%20to%20cold%20chains%20for%20decades%2C%20but%20advanced%20versions%20are%20now%20permeating%20the%20industry.%20Cold-chain%20providers%20are%20ditching%20manual%20processes%20for%20AI-driven%20algorithms%20and%20exploring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkraft-heinz-microsoft-metaverse-logistics-investment-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edigital%20twins%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-evolution-software-companies-develop-ai-agents-workforce-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20highly%20automated%20operations%20even%20more%20autonomous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20it's%20a%2050-year-old%20technology%2C%20or%20whether%20it's%20a%20cutting-edge%20AI%2C%20technology%20is%20very%20pervasive%20in%20the%20cold%20chain%2C%26quot%3B%20Sudarsan%20Thattai%2C%20the%20chief%20information%20officer%20and%20chief%20transformation%20officer%20at%20Lineage%20Logistics%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221480b6c3-34d7-4099-908e-51ea2063929e%5C%22%3EThe%20cold%20chain%20warms%20up%20to%20predictive%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20Lineage%20uses%20AI%20is%20with%20decision%20algorithms.%20When%20a%20poultry%20shipment%20from%20Lineage%20customer%20Tyson%20Foods%20arrives%20at%20a%20warehouse%2C%20algorithms%20determine%20where%20to%20place%20products%20to%20minimize%20walking%20or%20driving%20distance%20in%20the%20warehouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20whole%20turkey%20likely%20won't%20be%20on%20store%20shelves%20until%20November%2C%20but%20deli%20meat%20is%20transported%20and%20sold%20year-round.%20The%20algorithms%20could%20direct%20forklift%20operators%20to%20place%20whole%20turkeys%20on%20a%20high%20shelf%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20warehouse%2C%20while%20keeping%20sliced%20turkey%20for%20sandwiches%20close%20to%20the%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20cuts%20down%20on%20the%20miles%20that%20I%20need%20to%20drive%20to%20pick%20that%20pallet%20and%20put%20it%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Thattai%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20want%20to%20bury%20the%20deli%20meat%20because%20now%20you're%20going%20to%20expend%20extra%20energy%20digging%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECold-chain%20provider%20Americold%20sees%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20interest%20in%20innovation%20across%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F12-cold-chain-logistics-startups-helping-deliver-vaccines-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecold%20chain%20sectors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rob%20Chambers%2C%20the%20company's%20president.%20Pharmaceuticals%2C%20fresh%20produce%2C%20and%20specialty%20foods%20often%20lead%20the%20way%20in%20tech%20adoption%20because%20of%20regulations%20and%20temperature%20sensitivities%20that%20require%20a%20highly%20controlled%20and%20actively%20monitored%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChambers%20said%20customers%20aren't%20necessarily%20asking%20Americold%20for%20AI%20by%20name%2C%20but%20they%20do%20expect%20%26quot%3Boutcomes%20that%20AI%20can%20help%20deliver%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-target-use-ai-to-prevent-inventory-shortages-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efewer%20stockouts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20quickly%20react%20in%20real%20time%20to%20any%20changes.%20The%20cold-chain%20company%20has%20invested%20in%20predictive%20analytics%20to%20better%20understand%20customer%20demand%20and%20changes%20in%20how%20food%20flows%20through%20the%20supply%20chain.%20That%20way%2C%20Americold%20can%20proactively%20plan%20its%20warehousing%20capacity%2C%20Chambers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnilever%2C%20which%20owns%20ice%20cream%20brands%20such%20as%20Magnum%20and%20Ben%20%26amp%3B%20Jerry's%2C%20also%20uses%20AI%20for%20prediction.%20The%20consumer%20goods%20company%20operates%20a%20cold%20chain%20that%20spans%2060%20countries%2C%2035%20production%20lines%2C%20and%203%20million%20ice%20cream%20freezer%20cabinets.%20Unilever's%20supply%20chain%20team%20analyzes%20weather%20inputs%20with%20AI%2C%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20forecast%20how%20much%20ice%20cream%20consumers%20might%20buy%20in%20specific%20regions.%20If%20a%20heat%20wave%20is%20coming%2C%20ice%20cream%20demand%20might%20soar%2C%20and%20the%20AI-based%20inventory%20systems%20could%20suggest%20decisions%20on%20how%20to%20allocate%20stock.%20The%20AI%20tools%20improved%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unilever.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-search%2F2025%2Fhow-ai-is-transforming-unilever-ice-creams-end-to-end-supply-chain%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforecast%20accuracy%20by%2010%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Sweden%2C%20as%20per%20a%20January%20report%20from%20Unilever.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20sales%20went%20up%2012%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20predictions%20not%20only%20guide%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-target-use-ai-to-prevent-inventory-shortages-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einventory%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20they%20also%20help%20managers%20determine%20the%20number%20of%20trucks%20needed%20and%20the%20optimal%20way%20to%20route%20them%20to%20and%20from%20warehouses%2C%20said%20Ron%20Leibman%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20McCarter%20%26amp%3B%20English's%20transportation%2C%20logistics%2C%20and%20supply%20chain%20management%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20this%20stuff%20has%20been%20done%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20It's%20just%2C%20AI%20does%20it%20differently%2C%20faster%2C%20and%20probably%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Leibman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a7d8d27a-f52f-450c-a501-b64aba4c140d%5C%22%3EThe%20cold%20chain's%20data-sharing%20black%20hole%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmericold%20and%20Lineage%20see%20potential%20for%20AI%20to%20expand%20in%20the%20cold%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmericold%20is%20exploring%20digital%20twins%2C%20which%20create%20a%20virtual%20duplicate%20of%20a%20warehouse%20used%20for%20simulating%20and%20planning.%20It's%20also%20looking%20into%20AI-guided%20robots%20that%20pick%20products%20in%20cold%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20temperature%20monitoring%2C%20the%20technology%20is%20already%20going%20beyond%20recording%20temperatures%20to%20sending%20alerts%20when%20temperatures%20go%20out%20of%20range%2C%20Thattai%20said.%20Large%20language%20models%20could%20be%20trained%20on%20temperature%20excursions%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20and%20cheaper%20to%20deploy%20AI%20and%20detect%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThattai%20foresees%20AI%20agents%20automatically%20adjusting%20warehouse%20appointment%20times%20based%20on%20a%20truck's%20real-time%20location%20data%2C%20rather%20than%20using%20estimates%20or%20phone%20calls.%20Thattai%20jokes%20that%20if%20he%20calls%20a%20truck%20driver%20to%20ask%20for%20their%20location%2C%20no%20matter%20what%2C%20they'll%20say%20they're%2010%20minutes%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20shortfall%2C%20however%2C%20is%20visibility%20and%20data-sharing%20across%20the%20cold%20chain.%20Thattai%20said%20it%20has%20progressed%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20ubiquitous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BData%20sharing%20is%20one%20big%20area%20which%20is%20a%20black%20hole%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20businesses%20share%20their%20real-time%20data%2C%20Thattai%20said.%20Independent%20or%20small%20trucking%20fleets%20may%20not%20use%20as%20much%20technology%20as%20large%20trucking%20companies.%20Produce%20growers%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20highly%20sophisticated%2C%26quot%3B%20Leibman%20said.%20They%20often%20work%20with%20manual%20documents%20listing%20the%20types%20and%20quantities%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20to%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20types%20of%20manual%20processes%20don't%20lend%20themselves%20to%20data%20sharing%20in%20the%20cold%20chain.%20Without%20data%2C%20AI%20lacks%20a%20basis%20for%20making%20predictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20really%20at%20the%20point%20of%20utilizing%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20its%20max%2C%26quot%3B%20Leibman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-for-cold-chain-operations-safety-algorithms-agents-digital-twins-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753118216000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687aaecbf748d8c055f5e941%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-for-cold-chain-operations-safety-algorithms-agents-digital-twins-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20cold-chain%20operations%2C%20AI%20algorithms%2C%20agents%2C%20and%20digital%20twins%20are%20helping%20warehouses%20manage%20operations%20and%20inventory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Shefali%20Kapadia)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-for-cold-chain-operations-safety-algorithms-agents-digital-twins-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Astronomer's%20interim%20CEO%20shares%20the%20silver%20lining%20of%20the%20viral%20Coldplay%20'kiss%20cam'%22%2C%22