es%2C%20stevia%2C%20and%20rose%20apples%20%E2%80%94%20is%20just%20an%20hour%E2%80%99s%20drive%20from%20the%20big%20city%20is%20almost%20unbelievable.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289450%2Fmumbai-couple-make-eco-friendly-farm-stay-in-nashik-with-mud-tiles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThis%20transformation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20not%20an%20overnight%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20points%20out%20Keyur%20Barad%20(38)%20and%20one-half%20of%20the%20entrepreneur%20brother%20duo%20who%20spearheaded%20this%20project.%20He%20clarifies%20that%20it%20took%20him%20and%20his%20brother%20Nishit%20(41)%2015%20long%20years%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctoil%2C%20sweat%2C%20time%2C%20savings%20and%20sheer%20perseverance%E2%80%9D%20to%20create%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20three-acre%20estate%20in%20Dahisar%20village%2C%20Manor%20taluka%2C%20the%20style%20mutates%20widely.%20While%20the%20farm%20and%20the%20surrounding%20food%20forest%20have%20earthy%20notes%20to%20them%2C%20the%20farmstay%E2%80%99s%20facade%20of%20wood%2C%20cane%2C%20ceramic%2C%20glass%2C%20metal%20and%20stone%20is%20in%20a%20luxurious%20contrast.%20But%20for%20the%20Barad%20brothers%2C%20the%20entire%20project%20is%20rooted%20in%20family.%20Everything%20else%20is%20secondary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20story%20is%20not%20just%20about%20Nishit%20and%20me%2C%20but%20about%20two%20brothers%20across%20two%20generations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Keyur%20says%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20father%20and%20uncle%20who%20laid%20the%20roots%20of%20this%20project%20in%202007.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20(Girdhar)%20bought%20the%20land%20for%20my%20uncle%2C%20who%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F322666%2Fretired-couple-turns-ancestral-land-into-eco-friendly-konkan-homestay-sindhudurg-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etur